{"tid":661014,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"頒令可由梅姐遺產提92萬還訟費 官勸「梅媽」：唔好搞咁多訴訟啦","createTime":"2018-05-11T07:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T07:39:11.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5a9cd6e3ea38f6db67febe3f0674cffa4a7a368","tid":661014,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KTnofy.QrNC2UlpfC9u3Dw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180511a125102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKTnofy.QrNC2UlpfC9u3Dw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180511a125102.jpg&h=ca9bb186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n庭頒令「梅媽」可由梅姐遺產提92萬還訟費。陳詠詩攝<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】已故樂壇天后梅艷芳的母親「梅媽」覃美金，因遺產問題打官司敗訴並拖欠訟費，於2012年被頒令破產及在前年解除，惟其破產期的兩名財產受託人，又指「梅媽」拖欠費用而再申請她破產。然而，「梅媽」所累積的訴訟費用卻仍未解決。<br />\n<br />\n「梅媽」今現身高院就處理訟費進行聆訊，法庭命令匯豐信託可從梅的遺產中提取共逾92.2萬元，以償還「梅媽」欠下的所有案件訟費，另外，因「梅媽」早前已支付13萬元，故匯豐信託亦要歸還予她，而2份法定追討書也被撤銷。法官陳江耀最後向「梅媽」謂：「你身體依家大不如前，行動又唔係咁利落，你保重身體，唔好搞咁多訴訟啦」。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：陳詠詩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A0%92%E4%BB%A4%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B1%E6%A2%85%E5%A7%90%E9%81%BA%E7%94%A2%E6%8F%9092%E8%90%AC%E9%82%84%E8%A8%9F%E8%B2%BB-%E5%AE%98%E5%8B%B8-%E6%A2%85%E5%AA%BD-%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E6%90%9E%E5%92%81%E5%A4%9A%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F%E5%95%A6-045000527.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A0%2592%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%25A2%2585%25E5%25A7%2590%25E9%2581%25BA%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%258F%259092%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%2582%2584%25E8%25A8%259F%25E8%25B2%25BB-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%258B%25B8-%25E6%25A2%2585%25E5%25AA%25BD-%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%2590%259E%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%25A4%259A%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E8%25A8%259F%25E5%2595%25A6-045000527.html&d=cvraUpSWqjSd0pn6kM4YLv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4c87b2e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A0%92%E4%BB%A4%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B1%E6%A2%85%E5%A7%90%E9%81%BA%E7%94%A2%E6%8F%9092%E8%90%AC%E9%82%84%E8%A8%9F%E8%B2%BB-%E5%AE%98%E5%8B%B8-%E6%A2%85%E5%AA%BD-%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E6%90%9E%E5%92%81%E5%A4%9A%E8%A8%B4%E8%A8%9F%E5%95%A6-045000527.html</a>"}]}